data.description: This beautiful FHA approved condo is located in a well established community situated atop of Signal Hill with scenic views of the city, hills and ocean. This warm and inviting condo is perfect for a first time buyer looking for a place to call their own or an astute investor looking for a solid investment. On the first level you'll find a gourmet kitchen with all the bells and whistles and you can also cozy up next to the fireplace in the living room. The first level also comes equipped with a half bathroom with a newer vanity and a storage closet. On the second level you'll find two very generous sized bedrooms with private bathrooms in both. With a private balcony off the primary bedroom, enjoy a cup of coffee to get your morning started or a glass of wine to wind down the evening while enjoying beautiful sunsets overlooking the city with the most amazing view. Other upgrades include, newer flooring, paint, ceiling fans, and countertops. The condo comes with two tandem parking spaces and storage, while the HOA covers a community spa, landscaping, maintenance, basic cable, internet, hot water, trash, and sewer. Conveniently located near shops, restaurants, Hilltop Park, The Beach, LBCC, CSULB, Costco, and more!
